Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Maitta, Maitta, Maitta...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Maitta, Maitta, Maitta...
